quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Twa Ha
  20,2,(Yewe Muhamadi) ntabwo twaguhishuriye Qur’an kugira ngo ikubere umuzigo
  20,3,Ahubwo (twayihishuye kugira ngo ibe) urwibutso kuri ba bandi bagandukira Allah
  20,4,(Iyo Qur’an) yahishuwe iturutse ku waremye isi n’ibirere bihanitse
  20,5,(Allah) Nyirimpuhwe uganje hejuru ya Ar’shi
  20,6,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi, n’ibiri hagati yabyo ndetse n’ibiri munsi y’ubutaka ni ibye"
  20,7,"Kandi n’ubwo warangurura ijwi (cyangwa ukavuga bucece, byose ni kimwe kuko) mu by’ukuri (Allah) azi amabanga ndetse n’ibyihishe cyane (kurenza ayo mabanga)"
  20,8,Allah! Nta yindi mana iriho ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse We. Afite amazina meza
  20,9,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) waba waragezweho n’inkuru ya Musa
  20,10,"Ubwo yabonaga umuriro nuko akabwira ab’iwe ati “Mugume aha! Mu by’ukuri ndabutswe umuriro, hari ubwo nabazaniraho igishirira, cyangwa kuri uwo muriro nkahasanga uwatuyobora (inzira).”"
  20,11,"Nuko awugezeho, yumva ijwi rimuhamagara riti “Yewe Musa!”"
  20,12,"“Mu by’ukuri ndi Nyagasani wawe, bityo kwetura inkweto zawe kuko uri mu kibaya gitagatifu cya Tuwa”"
  20,13,"“Kandi nagutoranyije (ngo ube intumwa). Bityo, tega amatwi ibyo uhishurirwa”"
  20,14,"Mu by’ukuri ndi Allah! Nta yindi mana iriho ikwiye gusengwa itari Njye. Bityo, jya ungaragira kandi unahozeho iswala kugira ngo unyibuke"
  20,15,Mu by’ukuri imperuka izaba. Nayihishe (ibiremwa byose) kugira ngo buri muntu azahemberwe umuhate we
  20,16,"Bityo, uramenye umuntu utayemera (imperuka) agakurikira ibyo umutima we ukunda, ntazakubuze kuyemera bitazakuviramo kurimbuka"
  20,17,"(Allah aramubaza ati) “Ese icyo ni iki kiri mu kuboko kwawe kw’iburyo, yewe Musa?”"
  20,18,"(Musa) aravuga ati “Ni inkoni yanjye nishingikiriza, nkanayimanuza amababi y’ibiti ngaburira intama zanjye, kandi mfite n’ibindi nyikoresha.”"
  20,19,"(Allah) aravuga ati “Yinage hasi, yewe Musa!”"
  20,20,"Nuko ayinaga hasi, ihita ihinduka inzoka ikururuka"
  20,21,(Allah) aravuga ati “Yifate kandi ntutinye! Turongera tuyigire (inkoni) nk’uko yari imeze”
  20,22,"“Unashyire ukuboko kwawe mu kwaha, kuravamo kurabagirana bidatewe n’uburwayi; icyo kiraba ari ikindi gitangaza”"
  20,23,“(Ibyo) ni ukugira ngo tukwereke bimwe mu bitangaza byacu bihambaye”
  20,24,(Allah aramubwira ati) “Jya kwa Farawo (umuhamagarire kwemera Allah). Mu by’ukuri akabije kwigomeka.”
  20,25,(Musa) aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Agura igituza cyanjye (kugira ngo mbashe gusohoza ubutumwa bwawe)”
  20,26,Kandi unyorohereze inshingano zanjye (umpaye)
  20,27,Unagobotore ururimi rwanjye
  20,28,Kugira ngo babashe gusobanukirwa amagambo yanjye
  20,29,Kandi umpe umwunganizi ukomoka mu muryango wanjye
  20,30,"(Ari we) Haruna (Aroni), umuvandimwe wanjye"
  20,31,Munshyigikize mu kunyongerera imbaraga
  20,32,Kandi umuhe gufatanya nanjye mu nshingano zanjye (zo gusohoza ubutumwa bwawe)
  20,33,Kugira ngo tubashe kugusingiza cyane
  20,34,Tunakwambaze cyane
  20,35,Mu by’ukuri wowe utubona bihebuje.”
  20,36,"(Allah) aravuga ati “Rwose ubusabe bwawe bwakiriwe, yewe Musa!”"
  20,37,"Kandi rwose, twari twaranaguhundagajeho ingabire zacu indi nshuro"
  20,38,Ubwo twahishuriraga nyoko ibyo twamuhishuriye (tugira) tuti
  20,39,"“Shyira (uwo mwana) mu isanduku maze uyinage mu mugezi, hanyuma umugezi uzayigeza ku nkombe, maze izatoragurwe n’umwanzi wanjye (Farawo) ari na we mwanzi we. Kandi naguhundagajeho urukundo rwanjye (yewe Musa), kugira ngo ukure nguhojejeho ijisho ryanjye (nkurinze).”"
  20,40,"(Wibuke) ubwo mushiki wawe yagendaga (agukurikiye maze akabwira abagutoraguye) ati “Ese mbarangire uwamurera?” Nuko tukugarura kwa nyoko kugira ngo yishime kandi ntakomeze kugira agahinda. Hanyuma uza kwica umuntu (w’umunyamisiri, utabigambiriye), tugukiza akababaro (igihe wicuzaga tukakubabarira, tukanagukiza imigambi y’abashakaga kukwica), nuko tukunyuza mu bigeragezo bikomeye. Nyuma waje guhungira mu bantu b’i Madiyani imyaka myinshi, nuko uza kugaruka (mu Misiri) nk’uko byagenwe, yewe Musa"
  20,41,Kandi narakwitoranyirije (ngo ube intumwa yanjye)
  20,42,"(Yewe Musa!) “Genda wowe n’umuvandimwe wawe (Haruna) mwitwaje ibitangaza byanjye, kandi ntimuzadohoke mu kunsingiza.”"
  20,43,Nimujye kwa Farawo (mumuhamagarire kwemera Allah). Mu by’ukuri akabije kwigomeka
  20,44,"Mumubwire amagambo yoroheje, wenda ashobora kwibuka (akemera Allah) cyangwa agatinya (ibihano)"
  20,45,(Musa na Haruna) baravuga bati “Nyagasani wacu! Mu by’ukuri turatinya ko yahita atugirira nabi cyangwa agakomeza kwigomeka.”
  20,46,(Allah) arababwira ati “Ntimutinye! Mu by’ukuri ndi kumwe namwe; ndumva nkanabona.”
  20,47,"Mumugereho maze mumubwire muti “Mu by’ukuri turi Intumwa za Nyagasani wawe, (udutumye) ngo urekure bene Isiraheli tujyane kandi ntubatoteze, kuko rwose twaje twitwaje igitangaza giturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe! Kandi amahoro nabe ku wakurikiye umuyoboro (utunganye).”"
  20,48,“Mu by’ukuri twahishuriwe ko ibihano bizaba ku wahinyuye akanatera umugongo (amategeko ya Allah).”
  20,49,"(Farawo) aravuga ati “None se Nyagasani wanyu ni nde, yewe Musa?”"
  20,50,"(Musa) aravuga ati “Nyagasani wacu ni uwahaye buri kintu ishusho n’imiterere, maze akakiyobora.”"
  20,51,(Farawo) aravuga ati “None se ababayeho mbere (bakaba barahakanye mbere yacu) bizabagendekera bite?”
  20,52,(Musa) aravuga ati “Ubumenyi bwabyo buri mu gitabo kwa Nyagasani wanjye. Nyagasani wanjye ntajya yibeshya cyangwa ngo yibagirwe.”
  20,53,"Ni We wabagiriye isi nk’isaso, anabashyiriramo amayira menshi ndetse anabamanurira amazi mu kirere (imvura), nuko tuyameresha ibimera by’amoko atandukanye"
  20,54,Ngaho nimurye (muri ibyo bimera) munabiragiremo amatungo yanyu. Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso (bigaragaza ubushobozi bwa Allah) ku banyabwenge